{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/01/01/10956_crt_5LR7z.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/01/01/10956_crt_5LR7z.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/01/01/10956_crt_5LR7z.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/01/01/10956_crt_5LR7z.jpg"},"name":"ナレーション","summary":"戏剧角色背着台上其他剧中人对观众说的话。也指影视片中的解说词。说话者不出现在画面上，但直接以语言来介绍影片内容、交待剧情或发表议论，包括对白的使用。","relation":"旁白","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/c5/cf/3976_prsn_4eb60.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c5/cf/3976_prsn_4eb60.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/c5/cf/3976_prsn_4eb60.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/c5/cf/3976_prsn_4eb60.jpg"},"name":"置鮎龍太郎","short_summary":"日本の男性声優、ナレーターである。青二プロダクション所属。血液型はO型。\r\n\r\n妻は声優の前田愛。置鮎は再婚となる。前妻は声優の永澤菜教。","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":3976,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":10956},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/78/39/166836_crt_Pbszz.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/78/39/166836_crt_Pbszz.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/78/39/166836_crt_Pbszz.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/78/39/166836_crt_Pbszz.jpg"},"name":"下呂ヒカル","summary":"殺しのプロ『使い手』の中でも最強格となる五大名家『毒使い』下呂家の跡取り。超一流の殺し屋。\r\n裏稼業に身を置くため恋愛経験は皆無で、女性が苦手。家を継ぐために必要にかられ婚活を始める。趣味は遊具菓子。","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/fb/a8/2404_prsn_i47IV.jpg?r=1773926038","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fb/a8/2404_prsn_i47IV.jpg?r=1773926038","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/fb/a8/2404_prsn_i47IV.jpg?r=1773926038","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/fb/a8/2404_prsn_i47IV.jpg?r=1773926038"},"name":"石谷春貴","short_summary":"日本的男性声优，宫崎县出身。毕业于Pro-Fit声优养成所，2022年1月1日移籍至大沢事务所。","career":["seiyu"],"id":2404,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":166836},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/68/1c/166837_crt_MjdKd.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/68/1c/166837_crt_MjdKd.jpg